#CAMERA 2
#phrase Hero  1
Your Excellency, I bring two pieces of news. One is bad: Captain Tilvar has been slain near the gates to the mines. The other is far better - the Wormheads have been killed!
#phrase Huber  2
Yes, of course I shall honor Tilvar with a minute of silence. But first of all I must write to the capital and report that under my capable governorship the threat to Ingos has been eliminated!
#phrase Huber  3
Actually, I think I shall mention your services in my report, so mayhap in about three months you shall receive an official citation!
